name: strawberry-graphql-split
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.225.1" %}

# handle undefined PYTHON in `noarch: generic` outputs
{% if PYTHON is not defined %}{% set PYTHON = "$PYTHON" %}{% endif %}

package:
  name: strawberry-graphql-split
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/s/strawberry-graphql/strawberry_graphql-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  # the SHA256 gets updated by the bot
  sha256: b330e7041815db32c6706a30557b936d042472fa0da18c78149aa6ed76ec95de

build:
  # the build number gets reset by the bot
  number: 0
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.8
  run:
    - python >=3.8

outputs:
  - name: strawberry-graphql
    build:
      noarch: python
      script:
        - {{ PYTHON }} {{ RECIPE_DIR }}/test_recipe.py
        - {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --no-deps --no-build-isolation
      entry_points:
        - strawberry = strawberry.cli:run
    requirements:
      host:
        - jinja2
        - pip
        - poetry >=0.12
        - tomli
        # TODO: clean this up when poetry figures it out
        - python >=3.8,<3.12.0a0
        - six
      run:
        - python >=3.8
        - astunparse 1.*
        - graphql-core 3.2.*
        - python-dateutil 2.*
        - typing-extensions >=4.5.0
    test:
      imports:
        - strawberry
      commands:
        - pip check
      requires:
        - pip
    about:
      home: https://strawberry.rocks
      summary: A library for creating GraphQL APIs
      license: MIT
      license_file: LICENSE
      dev_url: https://github.com/strawberry-graphql/strawberry
      doc_url: https://strawberry.rocks/docs

  - name: strawberry-graphql-with-aiohttp
    build:
      noarch: generic
    requirements:
      run:
        - {{ pin_subpackage("strawberry-graphql", max_pin="x.x.x") }}
        - aiohttp 3.*
    test:
      imports:
        - strawberry
        - strawberry.aiohttp
      commands:
        - pip check
      requires:
        - pip
    about:
      home: https://strawberry.rocks
      summary: A library for creating GraphQL APIs (with aiohttp)
      license: MIT
      license_file: LICENSE
      dev_url: https://github.com/strawberry-graphql/strawberry
      doc_url: https://strawberry.rocks/docs

  - name: strawberry-graphql-with-asgi
    build:
      noarch: generic
    requirements:
      run:
        - {{ pin_subpackage("strawberry-graphql", max_pin="x.x.x") }}
        - python-multipart >=0.0.7
        - starlette >=0.18.0
    test:
      imports:
        - strawberry
        - strawberry.asgi
      commands:
        - pip check
      requires:
        - pip
    about:
      home: https://strawberry.rocks
      summary: A library for creating GraphQL APIs (with asgi)
      license: MIT
      license_file: LICENSE
      dev_url: https://github.com/strawberry-graphql/strawberry
      doc_url: https://strawberry.rocks/docs

  - name: strawberry-graphql-with-debug
    build:
      noarch: generic
    requirements:
      run:
        - {{ pin_subpackage("strawberry-graphql", max_pin="x.x.x") }}

    test:

    about:
